                    <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-800 pb-2"><span class="text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Empleo directo en el sector</span><span class="text-emerald-500">~5.000 puestos</span></li>
                    <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-800 pb-2"><span class="text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Graduados UNICEN en carreras tech/año</span><span class="text-emerald-500">+400</span></li>
                    <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-800 pb-2"><span class="text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Exportaciones de software (est.)</span><span class="text-emerald-500">USD 80M+ anuales</span></li>
